# Fandom survey corpus — regenerable from scripts/fandom_wikis.yaml, and large
# (raw_wikitext per page + every infobox Template: page, per wiki). The curated
# datasets under processing_output/fandom/ stay tracked; this is the scratch
# survey, not a deliverable.
processing_output/fandom_corpus/

# Scratch audits at repo root; per-book audit logs under library/ stay tracked
/audits/
# Research eval outputs: per-book arm extractions + the oracle verdicts (STU-535)
research/*/arms/
# alias-eval: per-book adjudication verdicts + run log (STU-543). Regenerable by
# run_books.py; the judged numbers live in research/alias-eval/results.md.
research/alias-eval/verdicts/
research/alias-eval/run.log
# embedding-eval: masked mention windows + their encodings (STU-576). Regenerable by
# build_corpus.py from the processing_output caches, which are themselves gitignored.
research/embedding-eval/corpus/

# Local, per-machine agent notes
CLAUDE.local.md
